pepino
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:The cultivated tropical South American shrub <i>Solanum muricatum</i>, fam. Solenaceae, with sweet juicy, pale cream to orange fruit with longitudinal purple stripes; also known as Peruvian melon, melon shrub, melon pear; introduced into NZ before 1940.
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
